description: Serendipity Mobile Catering LLC is fully licensed, insured, and ServSafe Certified mobile catering/food truck.Serendipity Mobile Catering was founded by Chef William Gruesser to bring the highest quality food to your business, home, or off the curbside.  “Serendipity” truck is one of Indy’s most equipped catering/food trucks roaming the streets today.  Constantly customizing menus per event, you’ll need to follow us on the usual suspects of social media.
